    "*": "<tr>\n  <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"diff-lineno\">Line 151:</td>\n  <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"diff-lineno\">Line 151:</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"><div>===Buddhist===</div></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"><div>===Buddhist===</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">−</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-deletedline\"><div><del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">====Selfless</del> love<del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">====</del></div></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">+</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-addedline\"><div><ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">[[K&amp;#257;ma]] is sensous, sexual</ins> love<ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">. It is an obstacle on the path to [[enlightenment]], since it is selfish.</ins></div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">−</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-deletedline\"><div><del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">The</del> <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">definition of love in</del> [[<del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">Buddhism</del>]] <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">is</del> <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">wanting</del> <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">others to be happy</del>. This love is unconditional and it requires a lot of <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">courage and acceptance (including</del> self-acceptance<del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">)</del>.  This <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">definition means that 'love' in Buddhism refers to something</del> quite different from the ordinary <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">term of </del>love which is usually about attachment<del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">, more or less successful relationships</del> and sex; all of which rarely occur without self-interest. Instead, in Buddhism it refers to <del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">de-tachment</del> and the unselfish interest in others' welfare.<del class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\"> </del></div></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">+</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-addedline\"><div><ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">[[Adve&amp;#7779;a]]</ins> <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">and</ins> [[<ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">maitr&amp;#299;</ins>]] <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">are</ins> <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">benevolent</ins> <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">love</ins>. This love is unconditional and it requires a lot of  self-acceptance.  This <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">is</ins> quite different from the ordinary <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">'</ins>love<ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">'</ins> which is usually about attachment and sex; all of which rarely occur without self-interest. Instead, in Buddhism it refers to <ins class=\"diffchange diffchange-inline\">deattachment</ins> and the unselfish interest in others' welfare.</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">−</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-deletedline\"></td>\n  <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"diff-empty\">&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">−</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-deletedline\"><div>====Selfish love====</div></td>\n  <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"diff-empty\">&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">−</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-deletedline\"><div>Selfish or conditional love is the \"near enemy\" of love, because it can appear very similar to true selfless love.</div></td>\n  <td colspan=\"2\" class=\"diff-empty\">&#160;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"><div>===Hindu===</div></td>\n  <td class=\"diff-marker\">&#160;</td>\n  <td class=\"diff-context\"><div>===Hindu===</div></td>\n</tr>\n\n<!-- diff cache key enwiki:diff:version:1.11a:oldid:6544736:newid:6545061 -->\n",
